Source: pg-trickle
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), cargo, clang, libssl-dev, pkg-config
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/grove/pg-trickle

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-trickle
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-trickle
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Streaming stream tables for PostgreSQL 18
  pg_trickle turns PostgreSQL 18 into a real-time data platform with
  streaming tables and differential view maintenance, implemented as a
  Rust and pgrx extension.
  Full background scheduler and shared-memory functionality require loading
  pg_trickle through shared_preload_libraries.
